				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">After thinking about all the alternatives, this one seems to me to be one of the easiest and best answers. After, you can customize it (you DO want to change the default question right away).  Unless the spambot can incorporate a dictionary to look for keywords I don't see how they can beat this one.
<br />

<br />
